description:
Micpioneer Wireless Bluetooth Karaoke Microphones

♬ Multi-function Karaoke Microphone Speaker ♬
Wired, wireless and speaker 3 in 1 multi-function karaoke machine, you can use it as a wired mic, wireless mic and a bluetooth player!
This mic is compatible with almost all iOS & Android devices, tablet, PC and laptop, an excellent mic with various functions and stable compatibility.

♬ Fantastic Echo Effect ♬
Come with highest quality chipset with 3 layered anti-noise filter head, vivid reverberation & adjustable echo effect button. Brings you to your best singing performance.

♬ Your Mobile KTV ♬
Micpioneer wireless microphone speaker is your mobile Karaoke, you can use the machine at home, on your car, in the park and when you are in travel. Singing & music is always surrounding your life!

Bluetooth Connecting Instruction
1. Press the power button for about 2S, if you hear a short music sound, means it's on.
2. Turn on the Bluetooth on your device and aonnect with the karaoke machine named "Q37", if there's a prompt tone means you have connected successfully.
3. Play the music on your phone, then just enjoy it!

Product Specifications
● Color: Rose Gold
● Material: Aluminium Alloy
● Weight: 365g(12.87oz)
● Output Power: 6W (Speaker Output)
● Input Voltage: DC 5V
● Battery Capacity: 2200mAh
● Products Size: 9.45*2.95*2.36in
● Speaker Frequency: 100Hz-10KHz
● Transmission Distance: 10m(32.8ft)
● Power Supply: Build-in rechargeable Li-ion battery
